  EntityId: boss.general_director
  DisplayName: General Director
  Description: "The oldest of them all. He has been alone on the top floor for so
    long that he no longer remembers for sure what the original casino rules were.
    At some point, he stopped looking for them in the manual and started making them
    up. He enforces them with complete conviction and full bureaucratic authority.
    Whether they benefit or harm the player is just an administrative detail that
    doesn\u2019t factor into his judgment."
